      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable performance on the road. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of regular use, such as small surface scratches and light wear on the upholstery, the car remains clean and presentable. All major systems are fully functional, and it is ready for immediate use without any urgent repairs needed.",
