    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention project seekers and restoration lovers! This vehicle is ready for a complete transformation and offers a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking to build their dream car from the ground up. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a blank canvas waiting for your expert touch. Grab this diamond in the rough and start your next great automotive adventure today!",
