    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age through some expected wear and tear. The engine and transmission are fully functional, providing a steady ride, but you should expect some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible signs of use on the interior upholstery. There are a few small mechanical items that may need attention in the future, such as aging suspension components and a slow-leak in the air conditioning system. Overall, it is a budget-friendly option for someone looking for reliable transportation without the high price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 21000.0,
