    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and mechanical integrity. This specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by its dependable performance and well-preserved interior. Thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and safety, this automobile represents an outstanding investment for the driver seeking both reliability and sophistication. We invite serious inquiries to experience this benchmark of automotive value.",
      "price": 31500.0,
